<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-5542] Timer component - Should defer scheduling tasks during startup of CamelContext</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-5542</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We should defer scheduling timer tasks during startup of CamelContext. As they may fire very fast. We should defer this using a StartupListener just as we do with quartz component etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
